title: From the Manger to the Cross 1912 (Biography, Drama) directed by Sidney Olcott

sources.title: From the Manger to the Cross 1912 (Biography, Drama) directed by Sidney Olcott
sources.description:
The Greatest Story Ever Told - Witness the Life of Jesus Christ, from Birth to Crucifixion, to Resurrection.
An account of the life of Jesus Christ according to the New Testament, told as a series of tableaus interspersed with Bible verses. Following Jesus from his birth to his crucifixion. The film shows his miracles, his teachings, and his ultimate sacrifice. It is a story of faith, hope, and love that has inspired people for centuries.

Original title: From the Manger to the Cross 1912


Director: Sidney Olcott
Writer: Gene Gauntier
Stars: R. Henderson Bland, Percy Dyer, Gene Gauntier
Genres: Silent Film, History, Religion, Film Archives
